    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Prepare quantized model\n",
        "\n",
        "Enable k-bit fine-tuning utilities and gradient checkpointing so gradients flow correctly through the 4-bit model while reducing GPU memory usage."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "msGNYoAkqjh4"
      }
